<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="resize" id="resize">resize</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
Sintaxe:
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;string&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">void</span> resize<span class="br0">&#40;</span> size_type size, <span class="kw4">char</span> val <span class="sy1">=</span> <span class="kw4">char</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="br0">&#41;</span> <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>

A função resize altera o comprimento da string para size. Se val for especificado
então qualquer elemento criado será inicializado com o valor val.
Esta função corre em <a href="../../complexity" class="wikilink1" title="complexity">tempo linear</a>.
</p>

<p>
Tópicos Relacionados: <a href="capacity" class="wikilink1" title="br-pt:string:capacity">capacity</a>, <a href="size" class="wikilink1" title="br-pt:string:size">size</a>
</p>

